---
import Info from "./InfoCard.astro";
---

<section class="section-container py-24 md:py-32" id="about">
  <div class="mb-16">
    <p class="section-heading">About</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Background</h2>
  </div>

  <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-5 gap-16 items-start">
    <div class="lg:col-span-2">
      <img
        src="/assets/photo-1.avif"
        alt="Kevin Bravo"
        loading="lazy"
        decoding="async"
        class="rounded-xl w-full max-w-sm mx-auto lg:mx-0 object-cover aspect-[4/5] grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-500"
      />
    </div>

    <div class="lg:col-span-3 flex flex-col gap-10">
      <Info />

      <div class="space-y-4">
        <p class="text-surface-600 dark:text-surface-400 leading-relaxed">
          I’m <span class="text-surface-900 dark:text-surface-100 font-medium">Kevin</span>, a product engineer and MPA student from Caracas, Venezuela, building full-stack products, internal platforms, and AI agent systems. I commit with full agency and ownership to the projects I work on. Most of my work starts as an unclear product or operations problem and ends as production software that teams rely on every day.
        </p>
        <p class="text-surface-600 dark:text-surface-400 leading-relaxed">
          I take ownership from architecture through delivery and production support, move with a bias for action, and stay accountable for building systems that last. On the side, I also explore Solidity and EVM security, ZK proofs, and cybersecurity.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        <a
                    href="/me/ama"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium bg-surface-900 dark:bg-surface-100 text-white dark:text-surface-900 rounded-lg hover:bg-surface-800 dark:hover:bg-surface-200 transition-colors"
        >
                Read AMA
          <i class="bx bx-message-rounded-dots text-base"></i>

        </a>
        <a
                  target="_blank"

                  href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1PINAAnA8BhFLK9kcseb73KboYi4dsR31/view?usp=sharing"

          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium text-surface-600 dark:text-surface-400 border border-surface-200 dark:border-surface-800 rounded-lg hover:border-surface-300 dark:hover:border-surface-700 hover:text-surface-900 dark:hover:text-surface-200 transition-colors"
        >
            Check CV
          <i class="bx bx-download text-base"></i>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
